This paper is about a caching system for data warehouse and data mart systems, which are typically used in database management. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Databases). The paper also discusses optimization and algorithmic techniques, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with query response times and caching, which could be relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
